Package: grobblR
Title: The package intent on allowing users to build flexible and aesthetically pleasing PDF reports
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Calvin", "Floyd", email = "calvin.michael.floyd@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The grobblR package allows R users the ability to intuitively create 
  flexible, reproducible PDF reports comprised of aesthetically pleasing tables, 
  images, plots and/or text.
